WEBVTT

01:06.336 --> 01:10.778
=The Truth=

01:11.531 --> 01:14.072
=Episode 6=

01:15.563 --> 01:19.576
(Bowang)

01:23.660 --> 01:24.300
Excuse me.

01:24.780 --> 01:26.539
Where is the table reserved by Miss Han?

01:26.660 --> 01:27.339
Sir.

01:27.339 --> 01:28.060
Second floor.

01:28.060 --> 01:28.739
Thank you.

01:28.739 --> 01:29.500
No problem.

01:36.979 --> 01:37.739
Little Zhao.

01:43.339 --> 01:44.339
Where should I sit?

01:44.940 --> 01:45.979
- Next to her.
- Next to him.

01:48.379 --> 01:49.179
I'll sit there.

01:49.179 --> 01:50.780
Next to Little Zhao.

01:54.580 --> 01:56.379
Off duty now, let's have a drink.

01:57.060 --> 01:59.060
No alcohol. I might get called in.

02:00.099 --> 02:01.020
Alright.

02:01.020 --> 02:02.899
You guys are killjoys.

02:03.459 --> 02:04.660
Then I'll drink by myself.

02:04.660 --> 02:05.459
Yu.

02:05.860 --> 02:07.660
One pot of spirit and two colas.

02:07.660 --> 02:08.420
- Okay.
- Spirit?

02:08.420 --> 02:09.540
You're really something.

02:15.300 --> 02:16.260
I'll open it for you.

02:20.659 --> 02:21.459
I'm not drinking.

02:21.580 --> 02:22.380
I'll have water.

02:25.100 --> 02:25.659
I'll have it.

02:25.659 --> 02:26.980
I'll have it.

02:35.260 --> 02:36.659
Did you tell Little Qian

02:36.659 --> 02:37.659
that you're pursuing me?

02:38.619 --> 02:39.619
No.

02:39.659 --> 02:40.619
What for?

02:42.219 --> 02:43.820
You know I like Little Qian.

02:45.499 --> 02:47.179
I know you like Little Qian.

02:47.659 --> 02:49.459
But Little Qian doesn't like you.

02:49.659 --> 02:51.260
You're single, and I'm single.

02:51.459 --> 02:52.659
So I can pursue you.

02:52.659 --> 02:54.140
Don't need his permission, but yours.

02:54.140 --> 02:55.339
I haven't agreed.

02:55.339 --> 02:56.260
I know you haven't.

02:56.260 --> 02:57.380
That's why I'm pursuing you.

02:58.020 --> 02:58.659
Fine.

02:59.459 --> 03:00.659
You're paying today.

03:01.219 --> 03:01.899
No problem.

03:02.499 --> 03:03.860
This place isn't cheap.

03:04.619 --> 03:06.860
Officer, can your salary cover this?

03:06.860 --> 03:09.020
Don't worry. I've got Qian here.

03:10.140 --> 03:11.619
She owns this place.

03:11.980 --> 03:14.059
I opened this place for him.

03:33.020 --> 03:33.659
Try this.

03:34.899 --> 03:35.540
This.

03:35.659 --> 03:36.820
This is way too much.

03:37.820 --> 03:38.659
Not at all.

03:38.739 --> 03:40.939
You need nutrients. Eat more.

03:41.380 --> 03:42.659
All are your favorites.

03:43.939 --> 03:44.980
Just this once.

03:45.140 --> 03:46.260
Don't do this again.

03:46.380 --> 03:47.540
Too much to finish.

03:48.380 --> 03:49.059
You eat too.

03:50.739 --> 03:51.540
Got it.

03:51.540 --> 03:53.580
Next time, let's eat at my place.

03:54.739 --> 03:55.540
Your place?

03:57.059 --> 03:59.179
I opened a restaurant nearby.

03:59.179 --> 04:00.420
You know the ropes.

04:00.420 --> 04:01.980
Come try the food sometime.

04:02.860 --> 04:04.260
Why open a restaurant suddenly?

04:06.619 --> 04:09.059
You cops are busy,

04:09.059 --> 04:10.219
but you still need to eat.

04:10.580 --> 04:11.939
If you eat at my restaurant,

04:11.939 --> 04:12.939
I won't charge you.

04:18.060 --> 04:19.740
Actually, I wanted

04:20.020 --> 04:21.859
you to come eat often,

04:22.459 --> 04:24.979
then we'd see each other more.

04:28.260 --> 04:29.580
Han Zhao, I've told you.

04:29.580 --> 04:30.500
It won't work.

04:32.459 --> 04:33.580
Why not?

04:34.060 --> 04:35.580
We're both single and available.

04:35.820 --> 04:37.140
And I've got this.

04:40.620 --> 04:41.539
I support you

04:42.180 --> 04:43.180
to open a restaurant.

04:44.339 --> 04:45.659
But if you say it's for me,

04:46.899 --> 04:47.659
I won't accept it.

04:49.180 --> 04:49.979
Got it.

04:50.779 --> 04:52.459
Enough talk, just eat.

04:53.020 --> 04:54.180
Quit rambling.

04:56.020 --> 04:57.700
Eat this. Your favorite.

04:58.020 --> 04:58.820
You eat too.

05:02.979 --> 05:03.899
If you say so,

05:04.659 --> 05:05.859
I won't come again.

05:08.180 --> 05:08.979
Well...

05:09.580 --> 05:11.180
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

05:11.180 --> 05:12.979
Why only love Little Qian?

05:14.580 --> 05:15.899
You're not his type.

05:16.659 --> 05:18.060
Do you know his type?

05:18.140 --> 05:18.979
Of course, I do.

05:19.219 --> 05:20.380
He likes long-haired,

05:20.380 --> 05:21.459
gentle,

05:21.459 --> 05:23.620
simple,

05:23.620 --> 05:24.859
and delicate girls.

05:25.979 --> 05:27.260
You're not that type.

05:32.620 --> 05:34.140
You told him about Chen Yumo?

05:40.380 --> 05:40.899
This way.

05:43.539 --> 05:45.820
Mr. Pang, you're here.
The room your booked is upstairs.

05:45.820 --> 05:46.419
This way.

05:46.419 --> 05:47.020
Thank you.

05:48.979 --> 05:49.779
Please, this way.

05:50.260 --> 05:51.459
What would you like to eat?

05:52.779 --> 05:53.779
Salt-baked mackerel pike.

05:53.940 --> 05:54.500
Thank you.

06:04.219 --> 06:05.219
Pretty woman?

06:06.859 --> 06:07.659
Do you know her?

06:08.060 --> 06:08.859
Colleagues.

06:09.620 --> 06:11.140
Same department with us.

06:12.459 --> 06:14.620
I really underestimated
you police officers.

06:15.020 --> 06:16.620
Your spending level is quite high.

06:17.820 --> 06:18.899
I think Ziwu

06:18.899 --> 06:20.219
is here for another blind date.

06:21.140 --> 06:22.260
Blind date?

06:23.539 --> 06:24.700
That guy comes here often.

06:24.700 --> 06:26.219
He brings a different woman each time.

06:33.299 --> 06:34.260
I often

06:35.260 --> 06:36.299
come to this place,

06:36.940 --> 06:38.339
so I booked here.

06:39.020 --> 06:39.979
The environment is nice.

06:40.859 --> 06:41.820
Take a look at the menu.

06:41.820 --> 06:43.099
If you don't like it here,

06:43.099 --> 06:45.539
we can change another place.

06:45.859 --> 06:46.620
No need.

06:46.820 --> 06:48.099
Anything will do.

06:48.940 --> 06:49.539
Alright.

06:49.899 --> 06:50.979
Let's eat first.

06:51.099 --> 06:51.859
By the way,

06:52.260 --> 06:54.140
I booked a KTV room.

06:55.060 --> 06:57.060
After dinner, we can go sing songs.

06:57.740 --> 06:58.580
Mr. Pang.

06:59.180 --> 07:01.740
I need to explain something to you.

07:02.419 --> 07:03.539
Actually, I'm not interested

07:03.539 --> 07:05.979
in this blind date today.

07:06.339 --> 07:07.099
The reason I came

07:07.099 --> 07:09.339
is that I didn't want
to embarrass Mr. Zhao.

07:10.140 --> 07:11.260
After today's meal,

07:11.260 --> 07:12.140
I think

07:12.140 --> 07:13.899
we won't meet again.

07:14.459 --> 07:16.539
So let's split

07:16.979 --> 07:18.099
the meal cost.

07:21.820 --> 07:22.620
It's okay.

07:23.419 --> 07:25.140
Take a look at the menu and order food.

07:26.140 --> 07:27.380
I need to use the restroom.

07:33.140 --> 07:34.580
Sir, what would you like to order?

07:34.859 --> 07:35.419
It's okay.

07:35.419 --> 07:36.380
I'll go to the restroom.

07:39.180 --> 07:40.060
I'll take a leak.

07:42.500 --> 07:43.260
I'll go too.

07:47.380 --> 07:47.940
Wait,

07:47.940 --> 07:49.459
you two don't go to the same restroom.

07:49.459 --> 07:50.072
Well...

07:50.899 --> 07:51.539
Hello.

07:53.219 --> 07:54.140
Having a blind date.

07:55.160 --> 07:57.539
(Restroom)
A police, over thirty.

07:58.859 --> 08:00.979
I don't know why my mom knew her.

08:01.620 --> 08:02.299
Hello.

08:03.060 --> 08:03.659
Hello.

08:05.539 --> 08:06.779
But honestly,

08:07.180 --> 08:07.940
I probably won't

08:07.940 --> 08:09.539
get much benefit from this woman.

08:10.299 --> 08:12.219
I did some digging before I came.

08:12.580 --> 08:14.500
With her level and position,

08:14.500 --> 08:15.219
she can earn

08:15.580 --> 08:17.260
ten thousand yuan at most per month.

08:18.380 --> 08:19.620
What's the use?

08:22.740 --> 08:23.940
To put it harshly,

08:24.419 --> 08:25.820
if she were frontline,

08:26.260 --> 08:27.099
died in service,

08:27.099 --> 08:29.140
I could get a compensation
of hundreds of thousands.

08:29.580 --> 08:30.099
Really.

08:30.580 --> 08:32.939
Just a woman without feminine charm,
no fun at all.

08:37.144 --> 08:38.936
(Restroom)

08:43.980 --> 08:44.779
Who did it?

08:46.220 --> 08:47.220
Who beat me?

08:47.819 --> 08:48.500
Where are you?

08:50.500 --> 08:51.500
Don't dare to admit it?

08:51.500 --> 08:52.376
What happened?

08:52.376 --> 08:52.980
Where were you?

08:52.980 --> 08:53.819
Who's in charge?

08:53.899 --> 08:54.539
Took so long.

08:55.100 --> 08:56.779
No one leaves
until I get an explanation.

08:57.539 --> 08:58.500
Who's in charge?

08:59.620 --> 09:00.299
Call him over,

09:00.299 --> 09:01.659
or I'll call the police. Hurry up.

09:04.340 --> 09:05.620
Where's the person in charge?

09:06.140 --> 09:07.460
Call him over. Who hit me?

09:11.659 --> 09:13.340
Get me the surveillance footage now.

09:13.699 --> 09:14.380
Hurry up.

09:22.939 --> 09:24.179
Is this your car?

09:26.299 --> 09:27.179
My friend's.

09:29.980 --> 09:31.340
Sorry for causing trouble.

09:31.740 --> 09:33.100
Thank your friend for me.

09:33.539 --> 09:34.659
It's okay.

09:42.419 --> 09:44.620
I've seen the girl who had dinner

09:44.620 --> 09:46.380
with you today.

09:47.819 --> 09:48.620
Where?

09:49.779 --> 09:51.419
When you first came to the department.

09:52.220 --> 09:53.539
Right at the entrance.

09:54.419 --> 09:55.860
I remember it quite clearly.

09:55.860 --> 09:57.299
I remember she had

09:57.299 --> 09:59.740
a Japanese lunchbox wrapped in cloth

09:59.740 --> 10:00.860
in her hand.

10:02.460 --> 10:03.899
We grew up together.

10:06.179 --> 10:08.299
I can tell that girl really likes you.

10:09.340 --> 10:10.059
Ziwu.

10:10.699 --> 10:12.179
We're just friends.

10:27.579 --> 10:29.419
I wish she thought the same way.

10:34.179 --> 10:35.460
I forgot to warn that scum

10:35.460 --> 10:36.760
to stay away from my restaurant.

10:38.220 --> 10:39.140
After what you did,

10:39.140 --> 10:40.460
he'd never dare come.

10:41.179 --> 10:42.380
I bet he won't even come near

10:42.380 --> 10:43.220
the area.

10:43.299 --> 10:44.260
But anyway,

10:44.260 --> 10:45.699
you shouldn't have beaten him.

10:47.100 --> 10:48.899
Didn't you hear what Little Qian said?

10:49.340 --> 10:51.299
He's trying to exploit women.

10:51.299 --> 10:52.220
Not a chance.

10:53.100 --> 10:54.740
And I turned off the cameras

10:54.740 --> 10:55.460
near the restroom.

10:55.939 --> 10:57.100
Smart move!

10:57.179 --> 10:58.779
He has no idea who beat him.

11:00.020 --> 11:01.620
You didn't see the face of Little Qian.

11:01.939 --> 11:03.100
If I hadn't hit him first,

11:03.100 --> 11:04.340
he would've done it instead.

11:04.939 --> 11:05.740
Right.

11:07.340 --> 11:08.220
Has he been like this?

11:08.220 --> 11:10.059
So violent?

11:10.220 --> 11:11.500
Of course not!

11:13.260 --> 11:15.699
Little Qian has always been

11:16.340 --> 11:17.340
good at learning

11:18.260 --> 11:19.260
and gentle.

11:20.140 --> 11:21.899
He can cook

11:23.179 --> 11:24.260
and paint well.

11:24.539 --> 11:25.819
He was a track and field star.

11:27.340 --> 11:28.579
Total heartthrob!

11:29.939 --> 11:30.740
Really?

11:32.539 --> 11:33.819
Cross my heart.

11:34.939 --> 11:35.899
Let me tell you.

11:35.899 --> 11:38.340
Many people
had crushes on him back then.

11:38.340 --> 11:40.419
(There was a long line of admirers!)

11:40.980 --> 11:41.819
Little Qian.

11:41.819 --> 11:43.699
(If we were taking numbers,)

11:44.100 --> 11:45.059
(I'd be first in line.)

11:45.059 --> 11:46.899
Little Qian, fight for it!

11:54.260 --> 11:56.380
(But he only had eyes for Chen Yumo.)

11:57.980 --> 11:59.419
Because of Chen Yumo,

11:59.419 --> 12:01.460
he fell out with his parents

12:02.740 --> 12:04.299
and went to police academy,

12:04.579 --> 12:05.860
becoming a police.

12:06.260 --> 12:07.980
The most dangerous kind,
criminal police.

12:09.140 --> 12:10.179
After all these years,

12:10.539 --> 12:13.020
he'd chase any lead

12:14.299 --> 12:15.779
about Chen Yumo

12:16.020 --> 12:17.659
until he confirmed it was false.

12:18.100 --> 12:18.899
It's been ten years.

12:20.140 --> 12:21.939
You know he doesn't like you.

12:22.579 --> 12:24.179
Doesn't that hurt you?

12:28.579 --> 12:30.620
It hurts, of course.

12:33.140 --> 12:34.220
But I'm willing to wait.

12:35.020 --> 12:36.500
I'm still young, right?

12:37.899 --> 12:39.100
For someone I love,

12:40.740 --> 12:41.899
I'll take the chance.

12:47.980 --> 12:49.059
I'll grab more drinks.

12:57.304 --> 12:58.360
One.

12:59.020 --> 13:00.260
Already back?

13:02.980 --> 13:03.860
What are you doing?

13:14.380 --> 13:16.659
Little Zhao

13:19.260 --> 13:21.460
rides motorcycles and runs a restaurant.

13:21.460 --> 13:23.419
Where else could I find
such an amazing girl?

13:26.140 --> 13:26.899
I've decided.

13:27.699 --> 13:29.220
I need to earn more money.

13:29.899 --> 13:31.620
One meal cost me half a month's salary.

13:31.620 --> 13:32.299
That won't do.

13:32.299 --> 13:33.220
Can't keep this up.

13:34.419 --> 13:35.579
Where are you going?

13:37.260 --> 13:39.380
Are you sneaking off to see Little Zhao?

13:41.299 --> 13:42.779
Go on!

13:45.539 --> 13:47.299
I'll focus on earning money.

13:47.779 --> 13:49.340
Work hard. Earn big.

14:01.547 --> 14:03.896
(At the department or at home?)

14:04.012 --> 14:09.944
(Zhang Ziwu:
At the department or at home?)

15:17.539 --> 15:19.260
Ziwu.

15:20.340 --> 15:20.980
Lei.

15:22.620 --> 15:25.699
Little Qian's parents
are overseas, right?

15:26.659 --> 15:28.140
I've never heard him call them

15:28.140 --> 15:29.419
once in the dorm.

15:30.260 --> 15:31.620
What a distant family.

15:31.620 --> 15:33.740
But he and Captain Leng...

15:34.740 --> 15:36.620
Honestly, they're kind of similar.

15:37.620 --> 15:39.220
Men of few words, workaholics,

15:39.460 --> 15:40.340
avoid relationships.

15:41.179 --> 15:41.939
Talking to them

15:41.939 --> 15:43.419
is like pulling teeth sometimes.

15:46.500 --> 15:48.620
Can't figure out
what Little Zhao sees in him.

15:48.740 --> 15:50.020
He's handsome!

15:51.500 --> 15:52.380
Little Zhao?

15:54.980 --> 15:56.340
The girl from that restaurant?

15:58.059 --> 15:59.059
How do you know?

16:01.059 --> 16:03.020
She's really into Ye Qian.

16:03.020 --> 16:04.179
Don't get your hopes up.

16:04.980 --> 16:06.620
Something's going on.

16:06.699 --> 16:08.020
Hurry. Tell me!

16:08.220 --> 16:10.100
What is there to tell?

16:10.460 --> 16:11.500
Not promising?

16:11.980 --> 16:12.899
Unrequited love.

16:14.179 --> 16:15.020
How tough.

16:19.595 --> 16:22.443
(Shancheng Community, North Gate)

16:32.619 --> 16:40.152
(Eternal Love)

16:58.091 --> 17:04.024
(China Railway High-speed)

18:09.900 --> 18:11.020
I've booked the room.

18:11.020 --> 18:12.339
I'll pick him up tomorrow noon.

18:12.420 --> 18:15.220
Okay. I'll transfer you the room fee
via WeChat this afternoon.

18:15.619 --> 18:16.420
No need.

18:17.260 --> 18:18.539
He hasn't finished his homework.

18:18.539 --> 18:20.180
It's in the bag.
Tell him to do it, okay?

18:20.420 --> 18:21.940
Xiaoyu, be good, okay?

18:21.940 --> 18:23.260
I will pick you up tomorrow noon.

18:23.260 --> 18:23.819
Alright.

18:24.099 --> 18:24.819
I'm leaving.

18:28.500 --> 18:29.460
Where do you want to go?

18:30.020 --> 18:31.059
Let's go eat.

18:31.420 --> 18:32.440
What do you want to eat?

18:33.339 --> 18:34.260
Anything.

18:56.539 --> 18:57.260
Where's Master?

18:57.900 --> 18:58.660
He took leave.

18:59.260 --> 19:00.180
He took leave?

19:01.220 --> 19:02.059
Where did he go?

19:03.180 --> 19:03.980
He went to Shanghai.

19:08.099 --> 19:09.940
Well, could you give this to him for me?

19:18.900 --> 19:19.619
Thanks.

19:32.664 --> 19:35.480
(Theater Entrance)

19:39.180 --> 19:39.980
Are you a child?

19:40.220 --> 19:40.980
No.

19:40.980 --> 19:41.740
Is this fun?

19:41.900 --> 19:42.859
Yes.

19:43.339 --> 19:44.299
Why are you alone?

19:44.700 --> 19:45.619
Where's Little Qian?

19:45.619 --> 19:47.220
Something holds him up,
so he won't come.

19:48.220 --> 19:49.220
Why didn't you tell me?

19:49.220 --> 19:50.980
If I'd tell you, you wouldn't have come.

19:51.099 --> 19:51.619
Take it.

19:51.819 --> 19:52.500
What for?

19:52.619 --> 19:53.379
I'm leaving.

19:54.619 --> 19:55.660
Wait. You're already here.

19:55.779 --> 19:57.660
We can just watch it together.

19:57.900 --> 20:00.099
About that motorcycle case,
I've wanted to thank you.

20:00.099 --> 20:01.099
You thank me?

20:01.579 --> 20:03.500
Little Qian should be
the one thanking me.

20:03.539 --> 20:05.819
With our relationship,
it doesn't really matter.

20:05.819 --> 20:07.700
It took you a whole month
to recall that?

20:08.500 --> 20:09.579
I've been remembering it.

20:09.579 --> 20:11.020
But my actions got hindered.

20:11.020 --> 20:11.700
Look at my hand.

20:11.980 --> 20:13.579
I'm like a fortune cat.

20:13.579 --> 20:14.740
I can barely manage to eat.

20:15.700 --> 20:16.900
You can barely manage to eat.

20:17.059 --> 20:18.700
But you send me selfies every day.

20:18.819 --> 20:20.180
You fortune cat!

20:25.819 --> 20:27.379
You thank me by inviting me to a movie,

20:27.379 --> 20:28.900
and I bought the tickets?

20:29.220 --> 20:31.099
After the movie,
I'll treat you to dinner.

20:31.099 --> 20:31.980
Not a big deal.

20:41.900 --> 20:43.619
Relax. I'm shopping with my mom.

20:43.619 --> 20:44.579
I'll tell her now.

20:45.779 --> 20:47.700
Since when did I become your mom?

20:47.819 --> 20:49.500
Last time, you sent
Little Qian dumplings.

20:49.500 --> 20:50.059
I lied to him

20:50.059 --> 20:51.500
that my mom made them.

20:52.940 --> 20:54.779
And you told me he accepted them

20:54.779 --> 20:55.859
and really enjoyed them?

20:56.180 --> 20:57.619
He did accept them and eat them.

20:57.619 --> 20:58.819
And he enjoyed them.

20:59.500 --> 21:00.299
Si Yuanlong.

21:01.299 --> 21:02.660
Can you stop telling lies?

21:02.660 --> 21:04.180
Can I trust you to handle things?

21:04.339 --> 21:05.819
Yes! Of course.

21:05.819 --> 21:06.539
Absolutely.

21:08.339 --> 21:10.500
Are you wearing Little Qian's jacket?

21:11.859 --> 21:12.779
He gave them to me.

21:12.940 --> 21:13.500
How is it?

21:14.020 --> 21:15.660
Do I look better than him wearing it?

21:16.568 --> 21:17.299
W-Well...

21:17.299 --> 21:18.260
Talk about that later.

21:18.260 --> 21:18.980
Let's go watch it.

22:01.644 --> 22:06.680
