22:32.396 --> 22:34.648
(Zhang Ziwu: Have you seen Xiaoyu?)

22:34.648 --> 22:42.840
(Leng Qiming: Just had a meal with him.
He's doing homework now.)

22:42.924 --> 22:48.472
(Zhang Ziwu: Talk to him more.
Don't just stare at him.)

22:55.779 --> 22:57.020
Got a lot of homework?

22:57.500 --> 22:58.500
It's manageable.

23:00.020 --> 23:02.379
I've been swamped lately.

23:02.936 --> 23:03.619
Well...

23:03.779 --> 23:04.339
I know.

23:04.940 --> 23:07.220
Call me if anything's wrong.

23:07.660 --> 23:08.299
Nothing's wrong.

23:09.180 --> 23:10.859
How are you and your mom

23:11.940 --> 23:14.180
getting used to things over there?

23:15.420 --> 23:16.619
Dad, I'm doing homework.

23:25.779 --> 23:27.500
Want ice cream?

23:27.940 --> 23:28.940
Chocolate.

23:30.619 --> 23:31.139
Okay.

23:34.619 --> 23:35.220
I'll buy it.

23:50.956 --> 23:51.980
(Loyalty, Justice, Service, Dedication)

23:51.980 --> 23:52.579
Ye.

23:53.139 --> 23:53.980
- Chief Xu.
- Where's your master?

23:54.660 --> 23:55.420
Went to Shanghai.

23:55.700 --> 23:56.339
Shanghai?

23:58.139 --> 23:58.980
To see his son?

23:59.819 --> 24:00.740
Call him.

24:00.740 --> 24:01.579
Ask him to come back.

24:02.379 --> 24:02.940
Okay.

24:11.260 --> 24:13.339
Don't eat this often.

24:14.379 --> 24:15.059
Too fatty.

24:21.660 --> 24:22.619
I've paid for the room.

24:23.420 --> 24:24.420
I'll send you the money.

24:24.420 --> 24:25.260
- Don't bother.
- Let's go.

24:27.940 --> 24:28.700
Be a good boy.

24:29.139 --> 24:29.819
Let's go.

24:30.579 --> 24:31.379
Bye, Dad.

24:32.779 --> 24:33.700
How have you been?

24:34.220 --> 24:35.740
Had a nice time?

24:36.020 --> 24:37.740
Have you missed me?

24:38.139 --> 24:39.220
Did you bring me a gift?

24:39.220 --> 24:40.579
Of course.

24:40.579 --> 24:42.299
(Adopt With Love, Take Me Home)
How could I forget that?

24:56.420 --> 24:57.859
You guys are doing a charity event?

24:58.220 --> 24:58.740
Have water.

24:58.740 --> 24:59.260
Thank you.

24:59.420 --> 25:00.059
How strong

25:00.059 --> 25:00.740
the sunshine is.

25:00.859 --> 25:01.539
Thanks.

25:01.660 --> 25:03.220
Let's see. What kind of dogs are these?

25:04.500 --> 25:05.339
So cute.

25:05.460 --> 25:06.099
Have some water.

25:06.099 --> 25:07.180
- Hello, this is Jiao Lei.
- Here you go.

25:07.980 --> 25:08.980
What kind of dogs?

25:09.020 --> 25:09.859
Okay, I'll be there.

25:09.859 --> 25:10.819
Are they strays?

25:18.540 --> 25:23.960
(Ye Qian:
Urgent mission. Come back now.)

25:30.859 --> 25:31.660
Little Zhao.

25:33.180 --> 25:33.980
I've got a mission.

25:34.220 --> 25:35.099
I have to go.

25:35.660 --> 25:36.859
What do you mean?

25:36.859 --> 25:38.059
You insisted on watching.

25:38.059 --> 25:39.859
Now you want to leave me here
all by myself?

25:40.220 --> 25:41.099
I'm really sorry.

25:41.099 --> 25:42.420
That's just how my job is.

25:43.500 --> 25:44.539
Please forgive me.

25:44.539 --> 25:45.500
I owe you a meal.

25:45.779 --> 25:47.619
Aren't you off today?

25:47.779 --> 25:48.579
You're not leaving.

25:51.099 --> 25:51.779
I'm going.

25:58.579 --> 25:59.339
Everyone's here?

26:05.740 --> 26:06.779
Three days ago,

26:07.139 --> 26:09.220
within Beicheng County's jurisdiction,

26:09.220 --> 26:10.460
a homicide occurred.

26:11.220 --> 26:13.339
The victim, Wang Xiaole,
lived in Apartment 402,

26:13.339 --> 26:15.299
Building 10 of Shancheng Community,

26:15.660 --> 26:17.660
got murdered in her home.

26:18.660 --> 26:21.420
Beicheng CID requested assistance
from city police department.

26:21.579 --> 26:24.339
And after deliberation
by city police department leadership,

26:24.339 --> 26:27.700
our department and the forensic unit

26:27.700 --> 26:28.859
are assigned to assist.

26:28.859 --> 26:31.539
These two are from Beicheng CID.

26:31.779 --> 26:33.379
Let them brief us on the case.

26:33.980 --> 26:35.139
Just call me Sun.

26:35.139 --> 26:36.020
I'm Zhou.

26:36.216 --> 26:36.819
(Loyalty, Justice, Service, Dedication)

26:36.819 --> 26:38.020
Captain Sun, it's all copied.

26:38.020 --> 26:40.020
Good. I'll brief everyone.

26:42.027 --> 26:43.579
(Photos of Wang Xiaole)
The victim is Wang Xiaole,

26:43.619 --> 26:44.740
33 years old,

26:44.740 --> 26:47.579
a teacher at the Yunxi Health School.

26:48.260 --> 26:50.139
Her parents reported the case.

26:50.740 --> 26:52.420
According to her dad,

26:52.539 --> 26:55.660
around 9 PM on the night of the murder,

26:55.779 --> 26:57.660
he sent her a message.

26:57.980 --> 27:00.099
But he waited until the next morning

27:00.099 --> 27:01.139
and still got no reply.

27:01.420 --> 27:02.660
So he and his wife got anxious

27:02.660 --> 27:04.700
and went straight to her home.

27:05.688 --> 27:06.264
(Photos of Wang Xiaole)

27:06.315 --> 27:08.379
(Wang Xiaole's bedroom)

27:08.379 --> 27:09.688
This is the victim, Wang Xiaole.

27:10.980 --> 27:13.660
(Wang Xiaole's Bedroom)
This is the crime scene,

27:13.660 --> 27:15.099
the bedroom.

27:20.492 --> 27:23.832
(Wang Xiaole's bedroom)

27:26.660 --> 27:28.420
Long, that outfit
looks pretty sharp today.

27:30.539 --> 27:31.379
Double-check it.

27:32.139 --> 27:32.700
Okay.

27:35.740 --> 27:37.688
Are you crazy?
Why are you wearing my jacket?

27:39.379 --> 27:41.059
You gave it to me.

27:41.059 --> 27:42.539
Why can't I wear my own jacket?

27:43.579 --> 27:44.664
When did I give it to you?

27:45.339 --> 27:46.420
That day we had hotpot.

27:58.539 --> 28:00.260
You threw such a nice jacket away?

28:02.339 --> 28:03.379
Quit the nonsense.

28:04.299 --> 28:05.379
I threw this jacket away,

28:05.579 --> 28:06.579
not gave it to you.

28:06.579 --> 28:07.619
(Police)
You did throw it away.

28:07.619 --> 28:08.420
But I asked you

28:08.420 --> 28:10.339
to give it to me if you didn't want it.

28:10.339 --> 28:11.500
I asked you several times.

28:12.779 --> 28:14.339
I thought you were joking.

28:14.779 --> 28:15.819
Joking?

28:16.099 --> 28:18.059
Why would I joke about a nice jacket?

28:19.579 --> 28:21.020
It just had some frays.

28:21.260 --> 28:24.339
I fixed them and it's all good.
Throwing it away is such a waste. Look.

28:26.379 --> 28:26.980
Alright.

28:27.539 --> 28:29.020
Then don't wear it when I do.

28:30.619 --> 28:32.740
Fine. Tell me in advance,
I'll wear a different one.

28:32.819 --> 28:34.360
I don't want to wear the same as you.

28:45.180 --> 28:45.740
Captain Leng.

28:46.099 --> 28:47.339
The primary crime scene

28:47.339 --> 28:49.220
has been fully processed by our team.

28:50.020 --> 28:52.220
Tell me about this community.

28:54.260 --> 28:55.579
Shancheng Community

28:55.579 --> 28:57.460
was built over twenty years ago.

28:57.660 --> 28:58.539
The buildings are old.

28:58.779 --> 29:00.299
Look, over there.

29:00.420 --> 29:01.619
It borders a wooded area.

29:01.940 --> 29:03.619
It's pitch black at night.

29:04.339 --> 29:05.980
We immediately

29:05.980 --> 29:06.900
reviewed all accessible

29:06.900 --> 29:08.900
(Keeping pet in a civilized way)
CCTV footage from the community.

29:09.004 --> 29:09.619
(Keeping pet in a legal way)

29:09.619 --> 29:10.660
At the south gate,

29:10.940 --> 29:12.260
a suspicious person was spotted.

29:13.379 --> 29:14.900
However, his identity

29:14.940 --> 29:16.579
remains unknown.

29:37.460 --> 29:39.740
Fingerprints and footprints
from the hallway surroundings

29:39.740 --> 29:40.700
and living room

29:40.700 --> 29:42.420
have been re-collected.

29:42.420 --> 29:44.740
The entryway mat was taken
by Beicheng CID.

29:45.220 --> 29:47.299
A total of five bloody footprints
were found

29:47.379 --> 29:49.779
on the entryway mat
and in the living room.

29:50.059 --> 29:52.660
Details await further testing.

29:54.460 --> 29:55.099
Zhou.

30:44.099 --> 30:45.579
Based on bloodstain distribution,

30:45.579 --> 30:47.980
it's concentrated near the nightstand.

30:48.740 --> 30:50.660
The blood spatter
shows a high-velocity pattern.

30:55.539 --> 30:57.059
This indicates a powerful impact.

30:57.059 --> 30:59.192
I assumed the suspect
is a young or middle-aged male.

31:14.420 --> 31:16.940
Based on the stroke width,

31:16.940 --> 31:19.579
it was likely written
using a blood-soaked finger.

31:19.859 --> 31:21.180
But no fingerprints were left.

31:24.940 --> 31:25.619
Captain Leng.

31:27.180 --> 31:28.020
Take a look.

31:41.779 --> 31:42.539
Thoughts?

31:44.660 --> 31:45.900
The writing flows smoothly.

31:46.220 --> 31:47.220
The strokes are steady.

31:47.819 --> 31:49.260
And it's in standard script.

31:50.779 --> 31:52.619
What kind of person

31:52.779 --> 31:54.500
writes like this?

31:56.099 --> 31:56.819
Composed

31:58.740 --> 31:59.379
and calm.

32:02.539 --> 32:04.139
Probably well-educated.

32:05.379 --> 32:07.539
After committing such extreme violence,

32:08.139 --> 32:10.980
he still had composure
to write on the wall.

32:13.020 --> 32:14.660
I think he is someone meticulous

32:15.339 --> 32:16.379
and unflappable.

32:18.020 --> 32:19.460
It was likely premeditated.

33:34.828 --> 33:37.304
(Wench)

33:49.803 --> 33:53.560
(Asepsis Testing Room)

34:11.736 --> 34:13.496
(South Gate-03)

34:26.123 --> 34:29.752
(Wench)

34:46.764 --> 34:49.816
(South Gate-03)

35:05.100 --> 35:07.128
(Wench)

35:12.012 --> 35:17.496
(Wench)

35:22.059 --> 35:23.300
(Forensic Unit)

35:23.300 --> 35:25.099
Based on blood coagulation at the scene

35:25.099 --> 35:26.900
and livor mortis,

35:26.900 --> 35:28.380
(Blood details at the crime scene)
the exact time of death was...

35:28.380 --> 35:29.500
The time of death

35:29.500 --> 35:32.420
was between 12 AM

35:32.420 --> 35:34.059
(Blood details at the crime scene)
and 1 AM the next day.

35:35.619 --> 35:37.900
Resulted from acute cerebral hemorrhage.

35:38.579 --> 35:40.259
The victim's skull

35:40.259 --> 35:42.099
(Blood details at the crime scene)
shows a depressed fracture,

35:43.300 --> 35:46.380
matching the corner of the nightstand.

35:46.700 --> 35:47.288
(Blood details at the crime scene)

35:47.288 --> 35:48.619
We can infer

35:48.619 --> 35:49.739
the suspect

35:49.940 --> 35:52.539
grabbed the victim's head

35:52.780 --> 35:54.179
and slammed it against the corner.

35:55.860 --> 35:57.860
Repeated, forceful impacts

35:57.860 --> 35:59.619
ruptured the left pericallosal artery

35:59.780 --> 36:01.659
and the left central artery,

36:01.820 --> 36:04.120
causing massive intracranial bleeding
and victim's death.

36:04.219 --> 36:06.420
Other wounds on the victim's body

36:06.420 --> 36:08.820
were inflicted shortly after death.

36:10.028 --> 36:11.460
(Victim's wound details)

36:11.460 --> 36:13.739
There are seventeen wounds total

36:13.739 --> 36:15.139
on the victim's torso and limbs.

36:15.659 --> 36:16.380
Look.

36:16.380 --> 36:19.619
These seventeen wounds
are straight, sharp,

36:19.820 --> 36:21.820
(Victim's wound details)
and uniform in length.

36:22.579 --> 36:24.579
This requires the suspect

36:24.579 --> 36:26.579
to possess precise control.

36:27.099 --> 36:28.099
Moreover, I noticed

36:28.579 --> 36:30.659
during the cutting,

36:30.659 --> 36:32.300
a downward pressure was applied.

36:32.619 --> 36:35.020
This motion matches
a scalpel user's technique.

36:36.099 --> 36:37.739
No fingerprints were found on scene.

36:38.139 --> 36:40.536
The killer wore gloves

36:40.536 --> 36:42.380
both during the murder
and writing on the wall.

36:42.668 --> 36:43.500
(Blood writing on the crime scene wall)

36:43.500 --> 36:45.579
I compared common types

36:45.579 --> 36:48.020
like cotton, synthetic fiber,
cloth, leather,

36:48.020 --> 36:49.179
and latex gloves.

36:49.539 --> 36:52.420
Only non-absorbent types
can be dipped in blood for writing.

36:52.619 --> 36:53.380
After elimination,

36:53.380 --> 36:55.860
only leather and latex
remain possibilities.

36:56.259 --> 36:58.020
Leather gloves

36:58.020 --> 37:00.619
are typically bulkier than fingers.

37:01.139 --> 37:02.460
When I tried writing in them,

37:02.460 --> 37:03.900
caused by the finger squeezing,

37:03.900 --> 37:05.980
the writing shows breaks or distortions.

37:06.300 --> 37:08.659
Difficult to write words with
uniform strokes on the wall,

37:08.659 --> 37:11.096
let alone the fluidity of the writing
on the crime scene wall.

37:11.420 --> 37:12.280
Leather gloves out.

37:12.619 --> 37:13.780
As for the last possibility,

37:13.780 --> 37:16.059
latex gloves are characterized
by high elasticity,

37:16.059 --> 37:17.219
smooth surface,

37:18.020 --> 37:20.699
and fit closest
to the size of human fingers.

37:21.820 --> 37:24.300
I bought commonly available
latex gloves on the market.

37:24.900 --> 37:27.020
(Blood writing on the crime scene wall)
After testing with blood,

37:27.020 --> 37:28.380
I preliminarily assumed the killer

37:28.380 --> 37:29.940
wore medical latex gloves.

37:29.940 --> 37:32.059
These gloves have talcum powder on them,

37:32.619 --> 37:34.020
which has

37:34.020 --> 37:36.460
a certain adhesive effect on the blood.

37:36.460 --> 37:38.259
This can result in dripping blood trails

37:38.259 --> 37:39.860
(Wretch)
forming below the writing.

37:39.883 --> 37:41.380
(Suspect's shoe printings
left on the crime scene floor)

37:41.380 --> 37:42.300
Around the hallway,

37:42.300 --> 37:44.699
on the entryway mat
and inside the crime scene,

37:44.940 --> 37:47.420
a total of five footprints
were collected.

37:47.820 --> 37:49.500
All are of size 43,

37:49.500 --> 37:51.099
mold-soled sneakers.

37:51.460 --> 37:53.500
The tread pattern shows minimal wear,

37:53.500 --> 37:55.500
indicating the shoes
might be relatively new.

37:55.940 --> 37:57.619
However, because this type of product

37:57.619 --> 37:59.739
is extremely common on the market,

37:59.900 --> 38:01.139
it has little reference value.

38:01.739 --> 38:04.059
Due to the small number
of footprints collected

38:04.059 --> 38:05.099
and their discontinuity,

38:05.380 --> 38:07.780
we can currently only roughly
infer that the suspect is

38:07.780 --> 38:09.579
(Suspect's shoe printings)
a male of medium build.

38:09.980 --> 38:11.739
We cannot infer

38:11.739 --> 38:13.659
more specific physical characteristics.

38:15.500 --> 38:17.099
The Shancheng Community

38:17.099 --> 38:19.020
has cameras only at the main gates

38:19.020 --> 38:21.139
on the north and south sides
for vehicle access.

38:21.659 --> 38:23.500
Those at the side gates
on the east and west,

38:23.500 --> 38:26.139
and between buildings,
are just for show,

38:26.139 --> 38:26.900
not even powered.

38:28.139 --> 38:30.179
Colleagues from Beicheng

38:30.619 --> 38:34.020
had conducted
a preliminary review of the footage.

38:35.480 --> 38:36.739
(Suspicious individual entering/exiting)
The time of this individual

38:37.259 --> 38:39.500
entering and exiting
through the south gate

38:39.500 --> 38:40.940
matches the time of the crime.

38:42.099 --> 38:43.059
Thus, Beicheng CID

38:43.059 --> 38:44.980
identified this person
as the prime suspect.

38:45.035 --> 38:45.720
(Victim's ex-husband entering/exiting)

38:45.816 --> 38:46.460
Okay.

38:46.460 --> 38:48.099
From this image, we can see

38:48.099 --> 38:50.380
he's wearing exactly a pair of

38:50.380 --> 38:52.300
mold-soled sneakers.

38:52.300 --> 38:53.300
(Victim's ex-husband entering/exiting)

38:53.300 --> 38:55.699
This person is the victim's
ex-husband, Wu Da.

38:56.020 --> 38:57.500
Captain Sun's team has confirmed

38:57.980 --> 39:00.099
that Wang Xiaole's boyfriend,
Huang Chong,

39:00.099 --> 39:01.940
was working overtime at the company
that night.

39:02.500 --> 39:03.940
His colleagues can attest to this.

39:04.699 --> 39:06.460
Wang Xiaole's parents also stated

39:06.699 --> 39:08.420
that the two had a good relationship.

39:08.420 --> 39:10.420
Moreover, both are
in their second marriage,

39:10.420 --> 39:11.739
with no financial conflicts.

39:12.259 --> 39:15.820
However,
Wang Xiaole's ex-husband, Wu Da,

39:16.340 --> 39:18.420
was seen entering and exiting
the Shancheng Community

39:18.420 --> 39:20.216
at 9 PM and 10 PM
on the night of the crime.

39:20.380 --> 39:22.579
Wu Da's semen was indeed
found inside the victim.

39:23.020 --> 39:25.579
But there's no evidence
of forced sexual activity at the scene.

39:26.259 --> 39:27.619
All evidence suggests

39:27.619 --> 39:29.659
the sexual encounter was consensual.

39:30.420 --> 39:31.739
They were divorced,

39:31.739 --> 39:33.259
yet they maintained that relationship.

39:33.259 --> 39:34.739
We need to look into it.

40:09.340 --> 40:09.940
Wu Da,

40:11.340 --> 40:12.460
we're here today

40:13.259 --> 40:14.259
to learn more

40:14.259 --> 40:15.420
about Wang Xiaole.

40:21.900 --> 40:23.259
Where did you injure your hand?

40:25.179 --> 40:26.099
I forgot.

40:26.940 --> 40:28.780
Probably bumped into something.

40:35.115 --> 40:36.760
(Admission Letter)

40:37.099 --> 40:38.008
(Surgery, Surgical Nursing)

40:38.028 --> 40:39.000
(Vascular Surgery, Dermatologic Surgery)

40:39.000 --> 40:39.896
(Clinical Oncology)

40:40.619 --> 40:42.179
How did he get so drunk?

40:42.460 --> 40:45.659
He was also like this
during your previous questioning?

40:47.579 --> 40:48.259
Yes.

40:49.300 --> 40:50.059
He was like this.

40:50.420 --> 40:52.659
(Surgery, Surgical Nursing)
It's said that ever since the divorce,

40:52.659 --> 40:53.900
(Vascular Surgery)
he's been drowning his sorrows in drink.

40:53.900 --> 40:56.219
(Clinical Oncology)
He seems unable to accept this reality.

40:56.340 --> 40:57.500
Do you know Wang Xiaole?

41:01.099 --> 41:01.860
My wife...

41:03.020 --> 41:03.860
Ex-wife.

41:04.340 --> 41:08.059
What were you doing
from 12 AM on the 9th

41:08.619 --> 41:09.579
to 1 AM on the 10th?

41:10.619 --> 41:11.259
Drinking.

41:12.420 --> 41:13.460
Where were you drinking?

41:13.780 --> 41:14.739
Specific location.

41:18.579 --> 41:21.460
The flower bed at the north gate
of Shancheng Community.

41:21.900 --> 41:22.980
Can anyone verify that?

41:24.860 --> 41:25.539
Verify?

41:26.460 --> 41:27.300
Verify what?

41:28.340 --> 41:29.860
What exactly happened, Officer?

41:31.579 --> 41:33.940
You went to Wang Xiaole's place
last night, didn't you?

41:35.500 --> 41:36.420
Why did you go there?

41:39.500 --> 41:40.699
I just... We...

41:42.380 --> 41:43.219
I went to get...

41:44.619 --> 41:46.539
Wait, officer.
I'm feeling really unwell.

41:46.980 --> 41:48.539
Can you just tell me what's wrong?

41:55.980 --> 41:56.619
Here.

42:07.739 --> 42:08.380
Xiaole?

42:19.809 --> 42:23.302
♪Replacing the weight of tears
with that of sweat♪

42:27.096 --> 42:32.417
♪Covering the gunshot's sound
with wounds♪

42:34.490 --> 42:39.344
♪No one is born unyielding and strong♪

42:40.150 --> 42:43.297
♪But because someone
